---
import Layout from '~/layouts/PageLayout.astro';
import AccordionFAQ from '~/components/widgets/AccordionFAQ.astro';
import { PAGE_METADATA } from '~/utils/metadata';
---

<Layout metadata={PAGE_METADATA.faq}>

  <!-- FAQ Section -->
  <div class="section-padding">
    <AccordionFAQ
      title="Frequently Asked Questions"
      subtitle="Find answers to common questions about our profit management consulting services, methodologies, and client engagement process."
      tagline="FAQ"
      classes={{
        container: 'container-premium',
        title: 'section-title text-navy',
        tagline: 'section-tagline',
        subtitle: 'section-subtitle'
      }}
    items={[
      {
        title: 'What is Profit Management Consulting?',
        description: 'Profit Management Consulting is a specialized approach that combines financial analysis, operational optimization, and strategic planning to help organizations maximize profitability. We use proven methodologies to identify profit opportunities and implement sustainable improvements.',
      },
      {
        title: 'How long does a typical consulting engagement last?',
        description: 'Our consulting engagements typically range from 3-12 months, depending on the scope and complexity of your challenges. We work closely with your team to establish realistic timelines and milestones that ensure measurable progress throughout the project.',
      },
      {
        title: 'Do you work with small and medium-sized businesses?',
        description: 'Yes, we provide tailored solutions for organizations of all sizes. Our flexible engagement models and scalable methodologies allow us to deliver value to small businesses, mid-market companies, and large enterprises across various industries.',
      },
      {
        title: 'What industries do you serve?',
        description: 'We have extensive experience across 60+ industries including medical, food processing, manufacturing, real estate, retail, technology, and financial services. Our team adapts proven methodologies to meet the unique challenges of each sector.',
      },
      {
        title: 'How do you measure success and ROI?',
        description: 'We establish clear, measurable objectives at the project outset and track progress using key performance indicators. Our clients typically see 15-40% improvements in profitability, with detailed reporting and analysis provided throughout the engagement.',
      },
      {
        title: 'What makes your approach different?',
        description: 'Our approach combines academic rigor with practical experience. Led by Dr. Mohamed Amria with 26+ years of expertise, we apply research-based methodologies while collaborating with U.S. experts to ensure global best practices.',
      },
      {
        title: 'Do you provide training for internal teams?',
        description: 'Absolutely. We believe in building internal capabilities to ensure sustainable results. Our training programs cover financial analysis, profit management techniques, and strategic decision-making to empower your team long after our engagement ends.',
      },
      {
        title: 'How quickly can we expect to see results?',
        description: 'While comprehensive transformation takes time, many clients see initial improvements within 30-60 days. We focus on quick wins early in the engagement while building the foundation for long-term sustainable profit growth.',
      },
      {
        title: 'What information do you need to get started?',
        description: 'We typically require access to financial statements, operational data, and key performance metrics. During our initial consultation, we\'ll discuss specific data requirements and ensure confidentiality through appropriate agreements.',
      },
      {
        title: 'How do we begin working together?',
        description: 'Contact us for an initial consultation where we\'ll discuss your challenges and objectives. We\'ll then provide a customized proposal outlining our approach, timeline, and expected outcomes tailored to your specific needs.',
      },
    ]}
    />
  </div>

</Layout>
